name: Early In
query:
Select `tabAttendance`.`employee` AS "User ID:Link/Employee:100",
       `tabAttendance`.`employee_name` AS "Name:Data:100",
       `tabAttendance`.`attendance_date` AS "Date:Date:100",
       CONVERT(VARCHAR(10), `tabAttendance`.`in_time`,108) as TimePart

From
     `tabAttendance`
